title: Small worlds close up (Photo Ebook).pdf
description:
Crown / 1978 / Eng / Pdf / 64 pages / ISBN10 0517532891 / 11.9 MB

This collection of spectacular photographs of familiar objects gives us a glimpse into the unseen universe. Lisa Grillone and Joseph Gennaro have used the scanning electron microscope, a remarkable instrument that records the minutest detail on the surface of objects, to explore the invisible structure of everyday things
